cast.overview: Corinne (Barbie) is a young country girl who heads to Paris to pursue her big dream – to become a female musketeer! Never could she imagine she would meet three other girls who secretly share the same dream! Using their special talents, the girls work together as a team to foil a plot and save the prince. It's all for one and one for all!
cast.title: Barbie and the Three Musketeers

details.biography:
From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia

Willow Johnson (born April 3, 1977) is a Canadian voice actress working for the Ocean Productions based in Vancouver. She has performed the roles of several characters for many anime series. She is best known to many Rumiko Takahashi fans as the voices of Kasumi Tendo from the Ranma ½ series and Kikyo from the InuYasha series, both of who are from Takahashi's manga.
